---
// Projects component - Clean and simplified layout
---

<section class="projects">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Featured Projects</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Enterprise security automation and cloud infrastructure solutions</p>
    
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Browser Popup MDM Automation</h3>
        <p>Comprehensive cross-platform policy templates and automation scripts for browser management on Windows and macOS endpoints with Microsoft Intune integration.</p>
        <div class="tech">
          <span>PowerShell</span>
          <span>JSON</span>
          <span>PLIST</span>
          <span>Intune</span>
        </div>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="https://github.com/a-ariff/aglobaltec-website" target="_blank">Code</a>
          <a href="https://guides.aglobaltec.com/popup-policy-guide" target="_blank">Guide</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Intune Remediation Scripts</h3>
        <p>Production-ready PowerShell scripts for Microsoft Intune proactive remediations covering compliance, security, and performance optimization.</p>
        <div class="tech">
          <span>PowerShell</span>
          <span>Microsoft Graph</span>
          <span>Azure</span>
          <span>Intune</span>
        </div>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="https://github.com/a-ariff/cda3a49a" target="_blank">Code</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/a-ariff/cda3a49a#readme" target="_blank">Docs</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Azure Landing Zone</h3>
        <p>Enterprise-scale Azure landing zone implementation using Bicep templates with security baselines, governance policies, and compliance frameworks.</p>
        <div class="tech">
          <span>Bicep</span>
          <span>Azure</span>
          <span>ARM</span>
          <span>DevOps</span>
        </div>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="#" target="_blank">Code</a>
          <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/ebd0b36e/" target="_blank">Framework</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .projects {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .card {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }
  
  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
  
  .card h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .tech {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .tech span {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .links a {
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
  }
  
  .links a:first-child {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .links a:first-child:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }
  
  .links a:last-child {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }
  
  .links a:last-child:hover {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
  }
</style>
